Package: Multiomics.Preprocessing
Type: Package
Title: Preprocess Proteomics and Metabolomics Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Bradley",
           family = "Ward",
           email = "bradleyalexward@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides utilities for preparing proteomics precursor-level
    and metabolomics peak-level data for downstream analysis. The package
    supports missing value handling, MNAR or MAR classification, imputation,
    normalisation, batch correction, aggregation, and quality-control plots.
